### Sign In
POST http://localhost:5215/api/authentication/sign-in
Api-Version: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@riskscreening.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Get Current User
GET http://localhost:5215/api/authentication/me
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Supplier
POST http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers
Api-Version: 1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "legalName": "Acme Soluciones S.A.C.",
  "commercialName": "Acme",
  "taxId": "20512345678",
  "country": "PE",
  "contactPhone": "+51 999 888 777",
  "contactEmail": "contacto@acme.pe",
  "website": "https://acme.pe",
  "address": "Av. Javier Prado 1234, Lima",
  "annualBillingUsd": 150000.50,
  "notes": "Proveedor referido por el area de compras"
}

###

### Get All Suppliers (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Suppliers (with filters and pagination)
GET http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers?country=PE&status=Pending&page=0&size=10&sortBy=legalName&sortDirection=ASC
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get All Suppliers (search by legal name)
GET http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers?legalName=Acme
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Supplier by ID
GET http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete Supplier
DELETE http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Api-Version: 1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Supplier
PUT http://localhost:5215/api/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Api-Version: 1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "legalName": "Acme Soluciones S.A.C.",
  "commercialName": "Acme Peru",
  "taxId": "20512345678",
  "country": "PE",
  "contactPhone": "+51 999 777 666",
  "contactEmail": "ventas@acme.pe",
  "website": "https://acme.pe",
  "address": "Av. Arequipa 5678, Lima",
  "annualBillingUsd": 250000.00,
  "notes": "Actualizado con nueva informacion comercial"
}

###
